    "description": "Form Gran Colombia and own all land in the Gran Colombia, Andes, and La Plata strategic regions",
    "icon": "https://vic3.paradoxwikis.com/images/thumb/1/18/Achievement_grander_colombia.png/64px-Achievement_grander_colombia.png",
